Description: New Coach MINI Christie Cross-grain Leather Carryall Style - F57523 - Black Features Condition: New - With Tags Style Number: F57523 Style Color: Black Hardware Finish: Polished Light Gold Tone Hardware Exterior Material: Cross-grain Leather Interior Material: Sateen Fabric Exterior Description: Coach's Christie Carryall is one of their most popular silhouettes and is offered in a variety of sizes. This offer is for their "MINI", which is their smallest version. It is crafted in Coach's cross-grain finished leather with light golden tone polished hardware. Coach's iconic horse & carriage logo and removable leather hang tag accents the front. It has a flattened bottom panel. Interior Description: There are three main fully lined compartments. A center offers two open slip pockets with an open top and magnetic tab closure. On either side of the center is a fully zippered wall pocket. The back one offers an inner zippered pocket with Coach's creed and authenticity patch sewn inside. It has a drop ranging from 21 to 25 inches. MSRP: $350.00 Additional Information: Made by Coach for distribution via their Coach Factory Stores.
